1009
01:09:43.929 --> 01:09:45.419
Mi dispiace.

1010
01:09:47.533 --> 01:09:48.807
Si.

1011
01:10:08.960 --> 01:10:10.046
Howard...

1012
01:10:11.223 --> 01:10:13.535
